URL = http://www.plugandwear.com/

Plug and Wear first online material store for DIY e-garments, smart fabrics and interactive textiles components. 

The idea of this site came from the fact that we see a lot of wearable electronics on the internet, but very few sites where you actually can buy wearable DIY components.   

Our targets are:

*Creating a one-stop source for smart materials, electronic components, connectors, everything you need for DIY

*Developing products compatible to the [[Arduino]] platform. That means that you connect our fabrics to the Arduino and it works with no need of interfaces.

*Working under the open-source philosophy."


